The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to recover background from multiple images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves segmentation techniques, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). The use of iterative clustering and k-nearest neighbour method suggests the involvement of machine learning techniques, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image retrieval and analysis, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which can be categorized under cs.LG (Learning).
